<item>
            <title>[LU-12033] Git ignore generated *.install server and client files </title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-12033</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Building client or server DEB packages generates files:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
lustre-server-utils.install
lustre-client-utils.install&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;from description files &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
lustre-server-utils.install.in
lustre-client-utils.install.in&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Any modifications take place in *.install.in files, thus gitignore&lt;br/&gt;
the generated *.install files.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
